item.description:
I have been searching for a "real deal" medium to relay messages from the other side that charges a reasonable price and I found one! Annie Roy, who claims that mediumship runs in her family, her mother has the gift, and so does her aunt, the famous Sylvia Browne! Patti who is in our group has gone to her, and was VERY impressed....

This meet up is VERY limited, so please do not sign up unless you are sure you can go.

Each person will sign up for a 30 minute reading for $60.00 to be paid in cash at the day of the meet-up. I will be sending out a sign up sheet prior to the meet up.

Annie claims that everyone will get a message from the other side, even if there is no one you know who has passed on- messages can come from other places also, such as from ones spirit guides.
item.why: Annie Roy is Sylvia Browne's daughter, and the gift runs in her family- I have spoken to Annie, and she is utterly awesome!! The light comes through even on the phone :)
item.name: Crossing the Veil- Mediumship Reading with Annie Roy
